metadata.name: R3NLT genR5 #1
metadata.description: named genR5 - gen for genesis, gen for generation, gen for generative art - this first NFT collection marks the arrival of Renault to new playgrounds, with ambitions that go far beyond the mere drop it pays tribute to the genesis of the iconic R5, born in 1972, and opens up an exclusive perspective towards the future R5 in 2024  genR5 draws a link between past, present and future, with a limited edition of 3944 unique video 3D models
